{
  "stem": "15197.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And when my father, for instance, in his haberdash little business he already was faced that Poles was standing before his business and calling not to go in and not to buy in a Jewish stall.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So you were facing this kind of thing before Hitler really started the war.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I explain, first of all, that the roots are in the Church.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I give a lot of-- I blame the church behavior before the war and certainly during the war, and Poles were quite religious.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is-- I would say, it's rooted antisemitism for generations.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Even the history, the Poles.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were kings here and there who permitted or give the same all kind of laws easing up for the Jews.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But, in general, the history of Poland was quite antisemitic too.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But Jewish culture flourished in this country which was antisemitic.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jewish culture-- yes, it was the last hundred years when it flourished and it was a new development of Jewish writers and Jewish literature.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was at the time when the laws were easing up for the Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then it flourished because, in general, the Jews are quite cultural people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the first opportunity where they could develop a little bit of their own creativity was used at the utmost.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's why it flourished.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was in Poland the largest Jewish population in Europe.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Was about three and a half million Jews in Poland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I would say it was about 11 percentage of the Polish population.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As longer Hitler was settling himself in Germany, as stronger the antisemitism was being felt and seen in Poland.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And suddenly with outbreak of the war we felt it more.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mentioned before how my father was assuring us children that the Germans are not so terrible.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
